digital wallets, loan origination and repayment tracking. Smart contracts automate loan agreements and enforce repayment terms without manual intervention. By integrating mobile apps and digital ledgers, money lenders can offer borrowers convenient access and real‑time updates while maintaining regulatory compliance.\r\n\r\nEmbracing technology is not just about keeping up with trends; it is about ensuring the future of money lending in Uganda and the EAC. By partnering with Sanaa and using smart contracts, mobile apps and digital platforms, money lenders can expand financial inclusion, enhance trust and unlock new revenue streams in the digital economy.\";s:12:\"content_json\";N;s:12:\"is_rich_text\";i:0;s:14:\"featured_image\";s:50:\"blogs/HP97V89OxdZ1htPzcKCGKbt7AhLjCrFWX66fmw7s.png\";s:9:\"author_id\";i:21;s:6:\"status\";s:9:\"published\";s:8:\"featured\";i:0;s:12:\"published_at\";N;s:12:\"reading_time\";i:2;s:5:\"image\";N;s:10:\"created_at\";s:19:\"2025-11-07 20:16:32\";s:10:\"updated_at\";s:19:\"2026-01-06 04:05:33\";s:5:\"views\";i:93;s:5:\"likes\";i:0;s:6:\"shares\";i:0;s:5:\"saves\";i:0;s:9:\"bookmarks\";i:0;s:10:\"meta_title\";N;s:16:\"meta_description\";N;s:8:\"keywords\";N;s:14:\"ai_suggestions\";N;s:12:\"seo_analysis\";N;s:22:\"collaboration_metadata\";N;s:14:\"version_number\";i:1;s:11:\"category_id\";i:2;}s:10:\"\0*\0changes\";a:0:{}s:8:\"\0*\0casts\";a:8:{s:12:\"published_at\";s:8:\"datetime\";s:8:\"featured\";s:7:\"boolean\";s:5:\"views\";s:7:\"integer\";s:5:\"likes\";s:7:\"integer\";s:6:\"shares\";s:7:\"integer\";s:9:\"bookmarks\";s:7:\"integer\";s:5:\"saves\";s:7:\"integer\";s:12:\"reading_time\";s:7:\"integer\";}s:17:\"\0*\0classCastCache\";a:0:{}s:21:\"\0*\0attributeCastCache\";a:0:{}s:13:\"\0*\0dateFormat\";N;s:10:\"\0*\0appends\";a:0:{}s:19:\"\0*\0dispatchesEvents\";a:0:{}s:14:\"\0*\0observables\";a:0:{}s:12:\"\0*\0relations\";a:2:{s:6:\"author\";O:15:\"App\\Models\\User\":33:{s:13:\"\0*\0connection\";s:5:\"mysql\";s:8:\"\0*\0table\";s:5:\"us