t Options</strong></p><ul class=\"[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1.5 [li_&amp;]:gap-1.5 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-disc flex flex-col gap-2 pl-8 mb-3\">\r\n<li class=\"whitespace-normal break-words pl-2\">Up to 4 lines total: 2 lines above the date and 2 lines below</li>\r\n<li class=\"whitespace-normal break-words pl-2\">Perfect for adding department names, \"RECEIVED,\" \"PAID,\" or custom messages</li>\r\n<li class=\"whitespace-normal break-words pl-2\">Personalize to match your specific business needs</li>\r\n</ul><p class=\"font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]\"><strong>Easy Date Adjustment</strong></p><ul class=\"[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1.5 [li_&amp;]:gap-1.5 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-disc flex flex-col gap-2 pl-8 mb-3\">\r\n<li class=\"whitespace-normal break-words pl-2\">Quick-change rotating date bands with protective cover</li>\r\n<li class=\"whitespace-normal break-words pl-2\">Includes minimum 10-year date range</li>\r\n<li class=\"whitespace-normal break-words pl-2\">Keep fingers clean while changing dates</li>\r\n<li class=\"whitespace-normal break-words pl-2\">Smooth, effortless operation for daily use</li>\r\n</ul><p class=\"font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]\"><strong>Self-Inking Convenience</strong></p><ul class=\"[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1.5 [li_&amp;]:gap-1.5 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-disc flex flex-col gap-2 pl-8 mb-3\">\r\n<li class=\"whitespace-normal break-words pl-2\">Built-in ink pad for automatic re-inking after each impression</li>\r\n<li class=\"whitespace-normal break-words pl-2\">No separate stamp pad required</li>\r\n<li class=\"whitespace-normal break-words pl-2\">Capable of thousands of clear, consistent impressions</li>\r\n</ul><p class=\"font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]\"><strong>Durable Construction</strong></p><ul class=\"[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1.5 [li_&amp;]:gap-1.5 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-disc flex flex-col gap-2 pl-8 mb-3\">\r\n<li class=\"whitespace-normal break-words pl-2\">Heavy-duty plastic body for long-lasting performance</li>\r\n<li class=\"whitespace-normal break-words pl-2\">Precision-engineered mechanism ensures accurate imprints</li>\r\n<li class=\"whitespace-normal break-words pl-2\">Quiet operation suitable for any office environment</li>\r\n<li class=\"whitespace-normal break-words pl-2\">Smooth movement prevents hand fatigue during repetitive use</li>\r\n</ul><p class=\"font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]\"><strong>Replaceable &amp; Re-inkable</strong></p><ul class=\"[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1.5 [li_&amp;]:gap-1.5 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-disc flex flex-col gap-2 pl-8 mb-3\">\r\n<li class=\"whitespace-normal break-words pl-2\">Built-in ink pad is both re-inkable and replaceable</li>\r\n<li class=\"whitespace-normal break-words pl-2\">Available in 8 ink color combinations</li>\r\n<li class=\"whitespace-normal break-words pl-2\">Extends stamp life and reduces long-term costs</li>\r\n<li class=\"whitespace-normal break-words pl-2\">Replacement pad reference: R-532-7 or R-532D-7 (for two-color pad)</li>\r\n</ul><p class=\"font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]\"><strong>Eco-Friendly</strong></p><ul class=\"[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1.5 [li_&amp;]:gap-1.5 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-disc flex flex-col gap-2 pl-8 mb-3\">\r\n<li class=\"whitespace-normal break-words pl-2\">Made from 79-85% recycled materials</li>\r\n<li class=\"whitespace-normal break-words pl-2\">Environmentally conscious manufacturing</li>\r\n</ul><h2 class=\"text-text-100 mt-3 -mb-1 text-[1.125rem] font-bold\">Ideal Applications</h2><ul class=\"[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1.5 [li_&amp;]:gap-1.5 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-disc flex flex-col gap-2 pl-8 mb-3\">\r\n<li class=\"whitespace-normal break-words pl-2\">Date stamping incoming/outgoing mail and documents</li>\r\n<li class=\"whitespace-normal break-words pl-2\">Marking invoices, receipts, and payment records</li>\r\n<li class=\"whitespace-normal break-words pl-2\">Processing forms and applications</li>\r\n<li class=\"whitespace-normal break-words pl-2\">Quality control and inspection documentation</li>\r\n<li class=\"whitespace-normal break-words pl-2\">Library book returns and due dates</li>\r\n<li class=\"whitespace-normal break-words pl-2\">Medical records and file management</li>\r\n</ul><h2 class=\"text-text-100 mt-3 -mb-1 text-[1.125rem] font-bold\">Important Note</h2><p class=\"font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]\">Not recommended for glossy paper or non-porous surfaces, as ink may smear. For these materials, consider using a dry felt pad with solvent-based or pigment inks.</p><h2 class=\"text-text-100 mt-3 -mb-1 text-[1.125rem] font-bold\">Why Choose the R-532D?</h2><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]\">The R-532D combines reliability, customization, and ease of use in one compact tool. Its precision construction ensures professional results with every impression, while the self-inking design saves time and eliminates the hassle of separate ink pads. Whether you\'re processing dozens or hundreds of documents daily, this dater stamp delivers consistent performance you can count on.</p>\";}}',1767525789),('soko_product_v2_2605','a:2:{s:7:\"success\";b:1;s:4:\"data\";a:10:{s:2:\"id\";i:2605;s:4:\"slug\";N;s:4:\"name\";s:17:\"Samba OG sneakers\";s:15:\"thumbnail_image\";s:78:\"https://soko.sanaa.ug/uploads/all/aOoho9f2mNY74SvqDDLRAwCUAiRwzuRIg